name: Dog Pile Maze Game
blurb: Hours of fun await you. This game will make you race against the clock! Navigate the maze and take your dog outside before he\u2026Uh oh.

rewards.reward: THROW US A BONE!\r\nGet a FREE download of the game before it's officially launched! We will also make a donation to a dog shelter in your name.
DOGGONE IT!\r\nReceive the above, plus: Get our exclusive Dog Pile stickers! Use them to show the world how much \u201cI Love Dog Pile!\u201d

EARLY BIRD-DOG SPECIAL!!\r\nBe among our first supporters to donate $10 and you'll get: Two free downloads of the game before it's available to the public (one for you, one for a friend! Stickers to show off your Dog Pile pride! AND a free 12 pack of game coins. Hurry! Quantities limited!

HOT DOG!\r\nReceive everything above, plus: You\u2019ll get a custom-made Dog Pile dog collar for your own dog featuring our exclusive "i love rescue" design. (We\u2019ll need your dog\u2019s breed and neck measurement when you pledge!)

YOU’RE PAWESOME!
Receive the above, plus: Be seen around town sporting the ever-so-stylish "i love rescue" Dog Pile T-shirt!

Plus, you'll get a free 6 pack of game coins to buy yourself more time while you're playing Dog Pile!
RAISE THE RUFF!\r\nReceive the above, plus: We'll donate a 30 pound bag of premium dog food to a local no-kill shelter in your name and tweet about it. Thank you for helping homeless dogs!!

THANK YOU VERY MUTT-CH!\r\nReceive the above, plus: You get to be a beta tester!! Be the first to play the game, try to break it, tell us what works, what doesn\u2019t, give our programmer a migraine, and \u2013 get your name in the credits!

PRETTY, PRETTY FLEAS \u2013 ER, PLEASE?\r\nReceive the above, plus: Be a part of the Dogington Post \u201cBrainstormer\u2019s Roundtable\u201d when we plan and design our next game.\u00a0We'll also make a $100 donation in your name to the dog rescue of your choice.
B-B-B-BAD TO THE BONE!\r\nReceive the above, plus: Your own 32GB Apple iPod Touch \u2013 so you can play Dog Pile, of course!\u00a0And a $200 donation to the dog rescue of your choice.

BEST IN SHOW!\r\nReceive the above, plus: Your $2,500 pledge gets you the new Apple iPad with retina display, perfect for hours of addictive Dog Pile gameplay! Plus, a $250 donation to the dog rescue of your choice.

WE DOUBLE DOG DARE YA!\r\nReceive the above, plus: Imagine this: \u201cMan, it took me 4 tries to get past Buster\u2019s level! My dog pooped in the house three times!\u201d With your $5,000 or more pledge, a level of the game will be named after your dog, his likeness will become the icon for that level of the game, and his image will be prominently displayed during the entire length of play during that level.\u00a0Plus, we will deliver 300 pounds of dog food to a needy rescue!

YOU\u2019RE NUMBER 1 IN OUR \u201cNUMBER 2\u201d GAME!\r\nReceive the above, plus: Immortalize your own precious pup forever! An $8,000 (or more!) pledge gets your dog in the middle of the action! He will replace our dog, Scoop, as the \u201cpup that needs to poop\u201d in one level of the game. Does it get any better than that? In addition, we will donate 500 pounds of dog food in your name to a needy rescue!

SPLISH SPLASH YOUR DOG WAS TAKING A BATH! Corporations can get in on our game. For your pledge of $10,000 the opening Splash Screen to Dog Pile will display your company logo! Tens of thousands of dog lovers will see it every time they launch the game! Plus we'll thank you generously on our site and Facebook page. Then, we will donate 1000 pounds of dog food to a needy rescue in your name and alert the local news media when it is delivered.
